BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 150.72 590 Td (YOU ARE NOT ALONE) Tj ET
q 0.5 G 1 w 50 580 m 382 580 l S Q
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 50 555 Td (If you are holding this journal, you have experienced one of the) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (most devastating losses a human can face. The death of someone) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 50 521 Td (you love by suicide.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 50 490 Td (This grief is different. It comes with:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 65 465 Td (- Questions that may never be answered) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 65 445 Td (- Guilt that does not belong to you) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 65 425 Td (- Anger at the person you love and miss) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 65 405 Td (- Stigma that silences your pain) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 65 385 Td (- A loneliness that feels impossible to explain) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 50 350 Td (This journal is a safe space. There are no wrong feelings here.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 50 330 Td (Write as much or as little as you need. Skip pages. Come back.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 50 310 Td (Your grief is valid. Your love is real. You will survive this.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
