BT 0 g /F2 14 Tf 108.48 590 Td (THE UNIQUE GRIEF OF SUICIDE LOSS) Tj ET
q 0.5 G 1 w 50 580 m 382 580 l S Q
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 50 555 Td (Suicide grief is complicated by factors other losses don't carry:) Tj ET
BT 0.1 g /F2 10 Tf 50 530 Td (The 'Why':) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F1 10 Tf 50 514 Td (The endless search for reasons that may never fully satisfy.) Tj ET
BT 0.1 g /F2 10 Tf 50 488 Td (The 'If Only':) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F1 10 Tf 50 472 Td (Replaying moments, wondering if you missed signs.) Tj ET
BT 0.1 g /F2 10 Tf 50 446 Td (The Stigma:) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F1 10 Tf 50 430 Td (Others may not know what to say, or say hurtful things.) Tj ET
BT 0.1 g /F2 10 Tf 50 404 Td (The Anger:) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F1 10 Tf 50 388 Td (It's okay to be angry at someone you love and mourn.) Tj ET
BT 0.1 g /F2 10 Tf 50 362 Td (The Guilt:) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F1 10 Tf 50 346 Td (Survivor's guilt is universal in suicide loss - and undeserved.) Tj ET
BT 0.1 g /F2 10 Tf 50 320 Td (The Trauma:) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F1 10 Tf 50 304 Td (You may have found them. You may replay the notification.) Tj ET

