BT 0 g /F2 12 Tf 109.44 590 Td (COMMON MYTHS ABOUT SUICIDE - DEBUNKED) Tj ET
q 0.5 G 1 w 50 580 m 382 580 l S Q
BT 0.1 g /F2 9 Tf 50 555 Td (MYTH: It was selfish.) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F4 9 Tf 50 539 Td (TRUTH: They were in unbearable pain and saw no other way out.) Tj ET
BT 0.1 g /F2 9 Tf 50 511 Td (MYTH: You should have seen the signs.) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F4 9 Tf 50 495 Td (TRUTH: Many people hide their pain. This is not your fault.) Tj ET
BT 0.1 g /F2 9 Tf 50 467 Td (MYTH: Talking about it is dangerous.) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F4 9 Tf 50 451 Td (TRUTH: Open conversation reduces stigma and saves lives.) Tj ET
BT 0.1 g /F2 9 Tf 50 423 Td (MYTH: They didn't love you enough to stay.) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F4 9 Tf 50 407 Td (TRUTH: Mental illness distorts thinking. Their love was real.) Tj ET
BT 0.1 g /F2 9 Tf 50 379 Td (MYTH: You'll 'get over it' with time.) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F4 9 Tf 50 363 Td (TRUTH: You learn to carry it differently. Grief has no timeline.) Tj ET
BT 0.1 g /F2 9 Tf 50 335 Td (MYTH: They are in a 'better place' \(if unhelpful\).) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F4 9 Tf 50 319 Td (TRUTH: You're allowed to be angry about platitudes.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
